evation load     *\n   vector for harmonic analysis with a hot start.                     *\n                                                                      *\n                        R.L. 11/9/95                                  * Subroutine to read in and initialize the elevation station load    *\n   vector for harmonic analysis with a hot start.                     *\n                                                                      *\n                        R.L. 11/9/95                                  * Subroutine to read in and initialize the global velocity load      *\n   vector for harmonic analysis with a hot start.                     *\n                                                                      *\n                        R.L. 11/9/95                                  * Subroutine to read in and initialize the velocity station load     *\n   vector for harmonic analysis with a hot start.                     *\n                                                                      *\n                        R.L. 11/9/95                                  * Subroutine to write out to the hotstart file (UNITS 67 and 68)     *\n   header information and the LHS matrix for the harmonic analysis    *\n                                                                      *\n                        R.L.  11/8/95                                 * Subroutine to write global elevation harmonic analysis RHS load    *\n   vector to a hot start file (UNITS 67 and 68)                       *\n                                                                      *\n                        R.L.  11/8/95                                 * Subroutine to write elevation station harmonic analysis RHS load   *\n   vector to a hot start file (UNITS 67 and 68)                       *\n                                                                      *\n                        R.L.  11/8/95                                 * Subroutine to write global velocit